Author: lessjesss
Text: people who haven’t had body image issues or struggles with food never understand it feels like i’m talking to a wall when i try to explain anything

Author: fouram444
Text: I can relate, only instead with my friend.  She thinks this "weightloss and intermittent fasting" stuff I'm doing is solely to lose weight.  She always asks what's wrong with my body, and that some people wish they could have it.  Like thank you, but that's not the only reason I'm doing this stuff ;(
